I am the Apothecary. I brew potions.
Do you need anything specific?

options.text: Can you make potions for me?
Talk about something else.

fc3a2f36-b366-430d-b6ea-f9dfee14c121.text: Can you make potions for me?

options.text: Have you got any decent gossip to share?
Do you know a potion to make hair fall out?
Have you got any good potions to give away?
No thanks.

c8500b6c-3819-4874-9393-e5fb5e1da77f.title: <player>
c8500b6c-3819-4874-9393-e5fb5e1da77f.text: Have you got any decent gossip to share?

7ffd4cf5-7486-43e6-9a93-29678c13c8bf.title: Apothecary
7ffd4cf5-7486-43e6-9a93-29678c13c8bf.text:
Well I hear young Romeo's having a little woman
trouble but other than that all's quiet on the eastern
front. Can I do something for you?

ed2d81de-4306-4751-bbe8-4ae5dd77e5fd.title: <player>
ed2d81de-4306-4751-bbe8-4ae5dd77e5fd.text: Do you know a potion to make hair fall out?

db0b6f5f-fe8a-4a32-96dd-07c1097707ec.title: Apothecary
db0b6f5f-fe8a-4a32-96dd-07c1097707ec.text:
I do indeed. I gave it to my mother.
That's why I now live alone.

deda4bb2-c76f-49ea-ab4b-6ca43667cd7b.title: Apothecary
deda4bb2-c76f-49ea-ab4b-6ca43667cd7b.text: But can I do something for you?

dd14d545-9a62-433e-b81a-f480f0c52f3f.title: <player>
dd14d545-9a62-433e-b81a-f480f0c52f3f.text: Have you got any good potions to give away?

841d61b7-e815-495a-8aeb-3428465e2de7.title: Apothecary
841d61b7-e815-495a-8aeb-3428465e2de7.text:
Sorry, charity is not my strong point.
Do you need anything else?

options.text: Talk about Romeo & Juliet.
Do you know a potion to make hair fall out?
Have you got any good potions to give away?
No thanks.

738f1b25-0c57-48e9-a04f-3bea43f98244.title: <player>
738f1b25-0c57-48e9-a04f-3bea43f98244.text:
Apothecary, Father Lawrence sent me.
I need a Cadava potion to help Romeo and Juliet.

06522dbb-65f1-4e53-9366-fb6195be3e28.title: Apothecary
06522dbb-65f1-4e53-9366-fb6195be3e28.text: Cadava potion. It's pretty nasty. And hard to make.

f0dd6c69-2eb6-46bf-bd90-424e89ee3555.title: Apothecary
f0dd6c69-2eb6-46bf-bd90-424e89ee3555.text:
Wing of rat, tail of frog.
Ear of snake and horn of dog.

60067f29-13f0-493e-8fd6-e722d0a9f80c.title: Apothecary
60067f29-13f0-493e-8fd6-e722d0a9f80c.text: I have all that, but I need some Cadava berries.

fd75e97c-c3d7-42d3-92b5-475ee35e5861.title: Apothecary
fd75e97c-c3d7-42d3-92b5-475ee35e5861.text:
You will have to find them while I get the rest ready.
Bring them here when you have them. But be careful.
They are nasty.

45e93678-72be-405f-a3e8-2f5fca780a45.text:
You hand over the berries, which the Apothecary shakes
up in a vial of strange liquid.

ca337aea-1a76-4517-a15a-e19a7975a5f2.title: Apothecary
ca337aea-1a76-4517-a15a-e19a7975a5f2.text: Phew! Here is what you need.

4dd0e65c-ad87-44bf-96c8-6d386f704ca4.text: The Apothecary gives you a Cadava potion.

options.text: What do these berries look like?
Where can I get these berries?
How are these berries dangerous?
Ok, thanks.

1657d6d7-0ccb-4699-9145-ce6d2a89c59e.title: <player>
1657d6d7-0ccb-4699-9145-ce6d2a89c59e.text: What do these berries look like?

cf9aeede-16f8-42be-906c-434d65136775.title: Apothecary
cf9aeede-16f8-42be-906c-434d65136775.text:
They're a nice bright pink colour, with green leaves,
stalks are a pale brown colour...you can't miss them.
They look pretty tasty, but I wouldn't advise eating them.

23d31753-5d65-4792-ad5f-7c9b83bd39b7.title: <player>
23d31753-5d65-4792-ad5f-7c9b83bd39b7.text: Where can I get these berries?

9f4549c2-217f-4594-924f-90fbca60773e.title: Apothecary
9f4549c2-217f-4594-924f-90fbca60773e.text:
I think I saw some recently in the local vicinity.
Oh yes, that's right! There was a little bit of commotion
when some kids visited the south eastern Varrock mining pit.
The trip was disrupted because some kids

783b0de0-f18a-4971-a5bf-a198e1901009.title: Apothecary
783b0de0-f18a-4971-a5bf-a198e1901009.text:
had found some cadavaberry bushes and they started 
picking them.  They wrapped that trip up pretty quickly!

6a7605f6-fe82-47a2-84d5-8a7d865f2384.title: Apothecary
6a7605f6-fe82-47a2-84d5-8a7d865f2384.text:
Hmm, they're generally okay, but if handled improperly
they can be a bit nasty. And I certainly wouldn't 
advise drinking the potion!

2c24aaa1-f39e-4e28-b83c-d157b50e0bef.title: Apothecary
2c24aaa1-f39e-4e28-b83c-d157b50e0bef.text:
Keep searching for those Cadavaberries.
 They're needed for the potion.

7335de37-5d52-40b8-96b6-a20067463808.title: Apothecary
7335de37-5d52-40b8-96b6-a20067463808.text: Well done. You have the berries.

fd878f9b-0900-4fef-b140-49b476bda79b.title: <player>
fd878f9b-0900-4fef-b140-49b476bda79b.text: Thank you for the Cadava potion.

09a0f1d9-e138-4244-946d-436ec01e5941.title: Apothecary
09a0f1d9-e138-4244-946d-436ec01e5941.text:
You're welcome. I hope it helps that young
couple find happiness.
